{"tid":734913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB再炒9人,隸屬Repackaging部門","createTime":"2018-07-09T05:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T07:14:35.000Z","uid":17646,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"912f7d42dea1e3f7e4099fb2eefafaf8f3f810b7","tid":734913,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"除咗TVBI同埋體育部遭滅門，仲有Repackaging部門，全部10人留返1個，似乎都係要嚟做過渡時期工作。<br />\n<br />\nRepackaging係乜嚟？即係買咗啲外購節目返嚟再剪嘅部門。以後啲外購節目會唔會一刀不剪直出？定係將工作轉去剪片部門呢？<br />\n<br />\n消失咗嘅體育部由余小姐管，Repackaging就係珍姐管。睇嚟今次全面瘦身不分派別，傳聞娛樂新聞仲有配音組都要裁員&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"8026e98e0a1d3809e4eb09c3031759e38a7ac79f","tid":734913,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7dd6b09c4bac2e13f5038edbd64f7404dc2238","tid":734913,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b38237875cd5737faa87dbd97cbdd2e34c72e9d","tid":734913,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f0e80af842034827952c68a9bb7db7b0c6a5ff","tid":734913,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"不如cctbb 肯執笠先走上黎講喇 唔想知佢炒乜鳩部門"},{"pid":"a2bbe2c570c9defce3ebc854e99ca1e3f4a8d6ab","tid":734913,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6f0e80af842034827952c68a9bb7db7b0c6a5ff","tid":734913,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"不如cctbb 肯執笠先走上黎講喇 唔想知佢炒乜鳩部門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"十年之後啦"},{"pid":"96ea31d803f165dfa2bf79ae256a9f8421730d64","tid":734913,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6f0e80af84203482